item.title: MAC
item.description: Four years of active participation in a Service Organization. Almost countless events. Please pardon our mess. This page is still a work in progress. I have many projects that I am documenting simultaneously and am doing my best to be thorough and embed a lot of rich metadata so that you can click around based on what you find interesting. Please feel free to contact me if you want me to finish this particular page immediately.
